      "message": "This will work here in Skia builds, but you\u0027d better make sure you understand how it works in other GN environments.  They use this main top-level BUILD.gn, but not at the root like it is here... it\u0027s under third_party/skia or something.  So //third_party/vulkan doesn\u0027t mean ./third_party/vulkan, it means something more like ../vulkan in those environments.\n\nIf you always want to use this file, I think you can just make it relative, dropping the //.  If you want to use Fuchsia\u0027s //third_party/vulkan:vulkan, this is good as-is.",
